'''MSE-9 General Purpose Droids''' were [[MSE-series]] [[Droid/Legends|droids]] that often served as security guards. They were equipped with an [[electro photo receptor]], [[Audio sensor/Legends|audio sensor]], [[Holocamera/Legends|holocamera]], a retractable [[Manipulator arm/Legends|heavy manipulator]], and a retractable fine manipulator.

